## 3. Gafkalo Entrypoint "No Such File or Directory"

**User Prompt:**
```
026-03-11 23:45:51 exec ./entrypoint.sh: no such file or directory
2026-03-11 23:45:57 exec ./entrypoint.sh: no such file or directory
...
```

**Reply:**
`entrypoint.sh` had **CRLF line endings** (Windows-style). The shebang was being read as `#!/bin/sh\r`, so the kernel tried to run `/bin/sh\r`, which doesn't exist and caused the "no such file or directory" error.

The file is now converted to Unix line endings (LF). Rebuild the image and start again:

```bash
make kafka-start
```

Or with docker compose:

```bash
docker compose -f gateway-swap/dev/kafka/compose.yml build --no-cache arc_geo_gafkalo
docker compose -f gateway-swap/dev/kafka/compose.yml up -d
```

**Fix applied:** Ran `sed -i '' 's/\r$//' dev/kafka/gafkalo/src/entrypoint.sh` to convert CRLF to LF.

