## 7. SES17-Emulators: Port 5432 Already Allocated

**User Prompt:**
```
Error response from daemon: driver failed programming external connectivity on endpoint emulators_test_db (d96430115b19f0d09509652428ec2637e06c96a9d7219df3e4d3c790d4bf1786): Bind for 0.0.0.0:5432 failed: port is already allocated
